Top/Bottom 10 Email Campaign Dashboard 3
This Dashboard consist of 3 charts: Funnel Chat, Horizontal chat, and Heat Map

Navigation buttons are used to go the other dashboards and reset button to refresh the dashboard




1. Top 10 Email campaign                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Funnel Chart is used to represent the Top 10 Campaign Name.

  • The color shows details about Campaign name
  • The Size Shows sum of     Total email sent 


Filter on emails to exclude Null and all alI EMAIL and also filter on Campaign Name to select top 10 campaign Name by the sum of email sent


  •    The mark is labeled by % of total email sent along with the table


      2.Bottom 10 Email Campaign

  • We used Horizontal bars to represent the bottom 10 email,
  • The data is filtered on email, the view is filtered on Campaign Name
  • The marks are labeled by the sum of email sent.


 3. Top 10 People receiving emails

Sum of total email sent is broken down by CAI Group Name VS Email.

Both Color, size  and Marks show Sum of total email sent 

The view is Filtered on Email and CAI Group name
